content.description: **Built for Dynamo 1.2 (Revit 2017)** LunchBox is a collection of reusable geometry and data management nodes.  The tools have been tested with Dynamo 1.2 and Revit 2017.  The tool includes nodes for surface paneling, geometry, Revit data collection, and more!.  After installation, search a 'LunchBox' category will appear in Dynamo.  For versions supporting Revit 2015 and 2016, please check an older release. For versions compatible with Dynamo 0.6, please install version 2014.6.5 or earlier.  For more information, visit http://provingground.io/tools/lunchbox/
